com.sun.identity.shared.whitelist

Class ResourceMatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.shared.whitelist.ResourceMatch

  • public class ResourceMatch
extends Object
    The class ResourceMatch defines the results of a resource match with respect to Policy.
